- (NSMutableArray *) scalingProcesses [read, write, retain]

The processes that you want to suspend or resume, which can include one or more of the following:

  • Launch
  • Terminate
  • HealthCheck
  • ReplaceUnhealthy
  • AZRebalance
  • AlarmNotifications
  • ScheduledActions

To suspend all process types, omit this parameter.
